name: Timberman (itch) (fertiz)
description:
Popular timberman game copy made in libGDX

Instruction:

  - Movement:

     - use LEFT ARROW to move the character to the left

    - use RIGHT ARROW to move the character to the right

 - Rules:

   - Don't hit the trees and be careful, the time is getting faster after every score.

Don't hit the trees and good luck :)
